spec.expr:
_stream:{fwb.type=$type,fwb.subtype in (${subtype:doublequote})}
| fwb.policy:(${policy:doublequote}) 
| $Logsql
| count() total_logs, count_uniq(fwb.policy) unique_policy, count_uniq(fwb.http_host) unique_http_host, count_uniq(fwb.server_pool_name) unique_server_pool_name, count_uniq(fwb.content_switch_name) unique_content_switch_name

_stream:{fwb.type=$type,fwb.subtype in (${subtype:doublequote})}
| fwb.policy:(${policy:doublequote}) 
| $Logsql
| stats by (fwb.src,http.response.status_code) count() results 
| sort by (results) desc 
| limit 10

Custom LogsQL filter attached to every query.
Set to "*" to not filter.
See https://docs.victoriametrics.com/victorialogs/logsql/
